Author: j4jackj
Text: I don't know how your case of disordered eating thinks but if it was me I'd just pick opt 1 and eat something digestible. In either case, plan to wake up earlier if you can, since the bike ride will take longer on a low restrict. ([TW fasting] >!I tried to ride a bike while fasting once. I was really slow, my muscles ached and my blood sugar went kinda high.!<)

Author: j4jackj
Text: I would eat something that you have found is easy to digest.
